          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-662-ROGP-line-1" n="1">Poor ladies! though their business be to play,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-ROGP-line-2" n="2">'Tis hard they must be busy night and day:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-ROGP-line-3" n="3">Why should they want the privilege of men,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-ROGP-line-4" n="4">And take some small diversions now and then?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-ROGP-line-5" n="5">Had women been the makers of our laws;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-ROGP-line-6" n="6">(And why they were not, I can see no cause;)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-ROGP-line-7" n="7">The men should slave at cards from morn to night;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-ROGP-line-8" n="8">And female pleasures be to read and write.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
